longest_message.longest_message: In a week's time, the game we all know and love so much will reach its tenth birthday. We want to invite you to join in on the **Terraria Tenth Anniversary Celebration! **  We are inviting everyone to share their favorite memories from the past ten years with Terraria. You laughed, you cried, you enjoyed the ride - now tell us all about it. The team is planning to hop in and reminisce alongside the community - and we are hoping to compile our very favorite community memories and stories into something that we can all look back on for years to come. You can share your Terraria memories in <#840307206133383168>   The entire Re-Logic team will be conducting an AMA on the r/Terraria Subreddit on May 17th, beginning at 10am Pacific Time. On top of that, be on the lookout for Re-Logic team members hanging out in Discord in the Terraria-Chat channel over the next couple of weeks.  **A VERY TERRARIAN BIRTHDAY PARTY CONTEST** This contest is all about your in-game building prowess. Show us your very best creations in game that fit the theme of celebrating Terraria turning 10 years old! Screenshots, videos of animated creations, whatever your mind can dream up, we want you to share it with us! This contest starts TODAY and will run through May 16th at 11:59pm Pacific Time  **TO TERRARIA WITH LOVE BIRTHDAY CARD CONTEST** This is your chance to craft a love letter to Terraria by way of Birthday Card. Create and share your very own 'Happy Tenth Birthday, Terraria' card, and you might just pick up one of those amazing pin sets below. Beyond the promise of prizes, though, is the chance to show the world how much Terraria means to you - and really, we just are looking forward to seeing them and trying not to cry. This contest starts TODAY and will run through May 16th at 11:59pm Pacific Time.  Share event entries at <#840371807030607912>   The Top 5 entries (as selected by us) for each event will get a full set of the really cool pins shown in the image.
